{
  "stem": "43.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She works [INAUDIBLE] blouse with the-- so I mostly was Polish.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Like, they don't understand Russian.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I understand Russian.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I decided [INAUDIBLE] was sitting also in-- over there was all the little owls.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Whenever I came, I was thinking the owls will fall-- fall fast.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But we was over there on some straw and all of the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So I told them we will-- we will go-- again, they-- we will go to the Russians.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the Russians, we not-- we're not afraid.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But there, Stalin was still [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So the-- the whole over there, the old boss was a [INAUDIBLE], was a Jew.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So we took-- for tomorrow, we took through-- three, me and two more.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we was going.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And told them the-- the story.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So he gave us work in a-- in the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You see, the kitchen came in from the-- from the-- from the war.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the soldiers are-- full of soldiers over there [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So he gave us in the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In the kitchen, we was all right.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We worked in the kitchen, and we eat in the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they made us-- he took-- he came and saw how we sleep.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I told him our little story.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He shall tell me [INAUDIBLE] to see what is here.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he came in, and he gave us places to sleep in-- in the houses.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And, you know, [INAUDIBLE] I was working near a year-- we was working in the-- in the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Then they told us that the Russian-- not-- not a full year, not a full year.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The-- we hear that the Russian, the kitchen is going to Russia.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So we don't want to go to Russia.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
